These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, amber
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, golf
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes amber is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate |
| Color   | amber | grey      |
| Sport         | golf    | biathlon      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts
2 different games are played: domino, backgammon
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person playing domino is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | singing      | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | adventure    |
| Game           | backgammon         | domino         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, funk
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the fan of soul is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Music-Genre         | soul | funk |
| Pet         | pony       | mouse       |
| Transport   | tram       | bus         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
There 2 different types of food: carrot, pear
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, gardening
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Food    | pear    | carrot     |
| Hobby       | camping    | gardening |
| Transport   | helicopter | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg
2 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Game       | mah-jongg | monopoly |
| Pet         | frog      | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike   |

